    <entry>
      <title>Arch Linux 安装后配置</title>
      <link href="/2023/01/07/archlinux-config/"/>
      <url>/2023/01/07/archlinux-config/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>ArchLinux 安装后并不是完事大吉了，还需要好好配置才能愉快的进行使用。</p><h2 id="配置源"><a href="#配置源" class="headerlink" title="配置源"></a>配置源</h2><h3 id="添加archlinuxcn仓库"><a href="#添加archlinuxcn仓库" class="headerlink" title="添加archlinuxcn仓库"></a>添加<code>archlinuxcn</code>仓库</h3><ol><li><p>添加文件：<code>/etc/pacman.d/archlinuxcn-mirrorlist</code>，添加内容：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Server = https://repo.archlinuxcn.org/$arch</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更多内容：参考<a href="https://github.com/archlinuxcn/mirrorlist-repo/blob/master/archlinuxcn-mirrorlist">国内仓库</a></p></li><li><p>修改文件：<code>/etc/pacman.conf</code></p><p>取消注释: <code>#Color</code>改为<code>Color</code><br>添加内容：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[archlinuxcn]</span><br><span class="line">Include = /etc/pacman.d/archlinux-mirrorlist</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>安装 GPG key：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -Syu</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S archlinuxcn-keyring</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>若安装失败，可以参考<a href="https://www.archlinuxcn.org/gnupg-2-1-and-the-pacman-keyring/">GnuPG-2.1 与 pacman 密钥环</a>重新生成密钥环。</p></li></ol><h3 id="配置aur"><a href="#配置aur" class="headerlink" title="配置aur"></a>配置<a href="https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Arch_User_Repository_(%E7%AE%80%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87)">aur</a></h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -S yay</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>以后就可以使用<code>yay</code>代替<code>pacman</code>了，语法完全一致，无需提前<code>sudo</code>，并且可访问<code>aur</code>仓库。</p><h3 id="安装扩展固件"><a href="#安装扩展固件" class="headerlink" title="安装扩展固件"></a>安装扩展固件</h3><p>为了让电脑充分发挥性能，在配置<code>aur</code>仓库后，应安装扩展固件：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yay -S mkinitcpio-firmware</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="配置控制台登录图形桌面"><a href="#配置控制台登录图形桌面" class="headerlink" title="配置控制台登录图形桌面"></a>配置控制台登录图形桌面</h2><h3 id="配置X11环境"><a href="#配置X11环境" class="headerlink" title="配置X11环境"></a>配置X11环境</h3><ol><li><p>安装<a href="https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Xorg_(%E7%AE%80%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87)">xorg</a>：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yay -S xorg-server xorg-xinit</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>修改<code>～/.xinitrc</code>文件，并添加内容，挑选自己的桌面环境添加：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">exec startplasma-x11       (kde-x11)</span><br><span class="line">exec startdde              (dde)</span><br><span class="line">exec gnome-session         (gnome)</span><br><span class="line">exec openbox-session       (openbox)</span><br><span class="line">exec startxfce4            (xfce)</span><br><span class="line">exec mate-session          (mate)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>修改<code>~/.bash_profile</code>(bash)或者<code>～/.zprofile</code>（zsh）文件，并添加内容：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">if [[ -z $DISPLAY &amp;&amp; $(tty) == /dev/tty1 ]]; then</span><br><span class="line">exec startx</span><br><span class="line">fi</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="配置Wayland环境"><a href="#配置Wayland环境" class="headerlink" title="配置Wayland环境"></a>配置Wayland环境</h3><p>wayland本身只是个协议，并不提供图形环境，因此需要安装混合器或直接安装有内置混合器的桌面环境</p><ol><li><p>KDE桌面环境</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yay -S plasma-desktop plasma-wayland-session</span><br><span class="line">startplasma-wayland</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>Gnome桌面环境</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yay -S gnome-shell</span><br><span class="line">gnome-shell --wayland</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>其他桌面环境自行搜索：<a href="https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Wayland">wayland</a></p><blockquote><p>某些应用程序是支持wayland协议，但是默认却走的xwayland，导致显示效果很不理想，可以设置环境变量或配置文件使其走wayland协议</p></blockquote></li><li><p>Firefox：<br>环境变量：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">MOZ_ENABLE_WAYLAND=1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>Chromium：<br>在<code>~/.config/chromium-flags.conf</code>中，添加以下几行:</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--enable-features=UseOzonePlatform</span><br><span class="line">--ozone-platform=wayland</span><br><span class="line">--enable-features=WebRTCPipeWireCapturer</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>qt程序：<br>需要额外安装：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yay -S qt5-wayland qt6-wayland</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后每次启动程序添加参数：<code>-platform wayland</code><br>或直接设置<code>QT_QPA_PLATFORM=wayland</code>，这样就不必每次添加参数</p></li></ol><h2 id="安装oh-my-zsh及插件"><a href="#安装oh-my-zsh及插件" class="headerlink" title="安装oh-my-zsh及插件"></a>安装<a href="https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh">oh-my-zsh</a>及插件</h2><ol><li><p>安装必备工具：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yay -S git wget</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>安装<code>oh-my-zsh</code>：<br>创建文件<code>install.sh</code>并写入以下<a href="https://gitee.com/mirrors/oh-my-zsh/blob/master/tools/install.sh">链接</a>中的内容<br>修改以下内容：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">Default settings</span></span><br><span class="line">ZSH=$&#123;ZSH:-~/.oh-my-zsh&#125;</span><br><span class="line">REPO=$&#123;REPO:-ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh&#125;</span><br><span class="line">REMOTE=$&#123;REMOTE:-https://github.com/$&#123;REPO&#125;.git&#125;</span><br><span class="line">BRANCH=$&#123;BRANCH:-master&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>改为：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">REPO=$&#123;REPO:-mirrors/oh-my-zsh&#125;</span><br><span class="line">REMOTE=$&#123;REMOTE:-https://gitee.com/$&#123;REPO&#125;.git&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>添加可执行权限：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chmod +x install.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>执行脚本进行安装：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">./install.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>安装历史记录插件和语法检查插件</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd ~/.oh-my-zsh/plugins</span><br><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-autosuggestions.git</span><br><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-syntax-highlighting.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>修改<code>~/.zshrc</code>文件，找到<code>plugins=(git)</code>，改为：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">plugins=(</span><br><span class="line">git</span><br><span class="line">sudo</span><br><span class="line">zsh-syntax-highlighting</span><br><span class="line">zsh-autosuggestions</span><br><span class="line">)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>使插件生效：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">source ~/.zshrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h2 id="安装输入法"><a href="#安装输入法" class="headerlink" title="安装输入法"></a>安装输入法</h2><ol><li><p>安装<a href="https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Fcitx5_(%E7%AE%80%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87)">fcitx5</a>：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yay -S fcitx5 fcitx5-chinese-addons fcitx5-gtk fcitx5-configtool</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>配置环境变量<code>/etc/environment</code>：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">GTK_IM_MODULE=fcitx</span><br><span class="line">QT_IM_MODULE=fcitx</span><br><span class="line">XMODIFIERS=@im=fcitx</span><br><span class="line">INPUT_METHOD=fcitx</span><br><span class="line">SDL_IM_MODULE=fcitx</span><br><span class="line">GLFW_IM_MODULE=ibus</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h2 id="配置开发环境"><a href="#配置开发环境" class="headerlink" title="配置开发环境"></a>配置开发环境</h2><h3 id="python"><a href="#python" class="headerlink" title="python"></a>python</h3><ol><li><p>下载pip</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yay -S python-pip</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>设置pip源</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip config set global.index-url https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="golang"><a href="#golang" class="headerlink" title="golang"></a>golang</h3><ol><li><p>安装<a href="https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Go_(%E7%AE%80%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87)">go</a>：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yay -S go</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>选择一个go工作目录，以<code>～/Develop/go</code>为例，新建三个目录：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir -p ~/Develop/go/&#123;src,bin,pkg&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>配置环境变量<code>~/.bash_profile</code>，zsh环境为<code>~/.zprofile</code>：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">export GOROOT=/usr/lib/go</span><br><span class="line">export GOPATH=~/Develop/go    # 这两行你需要</span><br><span class="line">export GOBIN=~/Develop/go/bin  # 修改为自己的</span><br><span class="line">export PATH=$PATH:$GOROOT/bin:$GOBIN</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改完成后，使环境变量生效：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">source ~/bash_profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>配置GOPROXY</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">go env -w GOPROXY=https://goproxy.io,direct</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h2 id="安装KDE桌面环境"><a href="#安装KDE桌面环境" class="headerlink" title="安装KDE桌面环境"></a>安装KDE桌面环境</h2><ol><li><p>最小化安装：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yay -S plasma-desktop</span><br><span class="line">yay -S plasma-nm plasma-pa kscreen bluedevil powerdevil kwalletmanager konsole</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>plasma-desktop</code>：基本的KDE桌面环境<br><code>plasma-nm</code>：网络管理模块，右下角的网络连接以及系统设置中的网络设置<br><code>plasma-pa</code>：声音模块，右下角的声音设置以及系统设置中的音频设置<br><code>kscreen</code>：屏幕管理模块，系统设置中的显示器配置<br><code>bluedevil</code>：蓝牙模块，启用需<code>systemctl enable bluetooth</code><br><code>powerdevil</code>：电源管理模块，系统设置中的电源管理<br><code>kwalletmanager</code>：KDE 钱包管理，一般用来禁用电子钱包<br><code>konsole</code>：KDE 的仿真终端</p></li><li><p>基本安装：<br>基本安装并不代表最小化安装，基本安装会附带很多程序，如桌面小工具、discover等</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yay -S plasma</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>安装KDE应用：<br>注意，这仅仅安装应用程序，并不会安装 Plasma 桌面。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yay -S kde-applications</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> ArchLinux </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Linux </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Arch Linux 安装NVIDIA驱动</title>
      <link href="/2023/01/07/archlinux-install-nvidia/"/>
      <url>/2023/01/07/archlinux-install-nvidia/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Nvidia 的开源驱动是作为逆向工程开发的，性能毕竟比不上闭源驱动，本篇教程将教大家在 ArchLinux 上安装闭源驱动。</p><h2 id="禁用-nouveau"><a href="#禁用-nouveau" class="headerlink" title="禁用 nouveau"></a>禁用 nouveau</h2><ol><li><p>编辑配置文件，没有则创建：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo vim /etc/modprobe.d/blacklist.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在最后一行添加：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">blacklist nouveau</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>生成新的 initrd：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkinitcpio -P</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h2 id="重启"><a href="#重启" class="headerlink" title="重启"></a>重启</h2><ol><li><p>执行重启命令：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">reboot</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>重启之后查看 nouveau 是否运行，没有输出代表禁用生效：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">lsmod | grep nouveau</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h2 id="停止可视化桌面"><a href="#停止可视化桌面" class="headerlink" title="停止可视化桌面"></a>停止可视化桌面</h2><ol><li><p>如果使用显示管理器，切换到其他 tty 进行关闭，如 lightdm：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo systemctl stop lightdm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>如果直接startx启动图形服务，退出窗口管理器即可，如 openbox 的<code>Log Out</code></p></li></ol><h2 id="安装驱动"><a href="#安装驱动" class="headerlink" title="安装驱动"></a>安装驱动</h2><ol><li><p>Arch Linux 可以直接安装 Nvidia 驱动：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -S nvidia</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>重启图形服务后检查：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nvidia-smi</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
